and more.</p><p><a href=\"x-help-action://openApp?bundleId=com.apple.iBooksX\" class=\"URL\">Open iBooks for me</a></p><div id=\"ibkse880f3cb\" class=\"Task no-header\"><div class=\"TaskBody\" role=\"region\" aria-hidden=\"false\" id=\"aria-ibkse880f3cb\"><ul class=\"ListSingle\"><li><p><em>Change the page view: </em>Open the book, then choose View&#xA0;&gt; Single Page or View &gt; Two Pages.</p><p>You can also drag the window&#x2019;s sides left or right until you see one or two pages.</p></li><li><p><em>See books in full-screen view: </em>Click the green full-screen button in the top-left corner. For more information about full-screen view, see <a href=\"https://support.apple.com/guide/?product=mac-help&amp;locale=en_US&amp;topicid=MCHL9C21D2BE&amp;type=ddm\" class=\"URL\">Use apps in full screen or Split View</a>.</p></li><li><p><em>Change the font size and style: </em>Move the pointer to the top of the book, then click the Appearance button <span class=\"NoBreak\"><img src=\"https://help.apple.com/assets/5A5401DF0946220B614CDC9D/5A5401E00946220B614CDCA4/en_US/2ff3169da3fb48799f822d17a44343ce.png\" alt=\"\" height=\"30\" width=\"41\" originalImageName=\"SharedGlobalArt/IL_Font_iBooks_osx.png\">.</span> Click a button to make the font smaller or larger, and choose a font under Book Font. </p><p>If the Appearance button isn&#x2019;t available, you can&#x2019;t change the book&#x2019;s font.</p></li><li><p><em>Change the page color: </em>Move the pointer to the top of the book, click the Appearance button, then choose White, Sepia, Gray, or Night.</p><p>If the page color options aren&#x2019;t available, you can&#x2019;t change the book&#x2019;s page color.</p></li><li><p><em>Change paragraph alignment: </em>Choose iBooks&#xA0;&gt; Preferences, click General, then select &#x201C;Let lines break naturally&#x201D; or &#x201C;Justify text.&#x201D;</p></li><li><p><em>Change hyphenation: </em>Choose iBooks&#xA0;&gt; Preferences, click General, then select or deselect &#x201C;Auto-hyphenate words.&#x201D;</p></li></ul></div></div><div class=\"LinkUniversal\"><strong>See also</strong><a href=\"https://support.apple.com/guide/?platform=mac&amp;product=ibooks&amp;vanityname=interact-with-video-audio-and-more&amp;version=1.11&amp;locale=en_US&amp;topicid=IBKSDA067BED&amp;type=ddm&amp;platformOSVersion=10.13\" class=\"xRef AppleTopic\">Interact with video, audio, and more</a><a href=\"https://support.apple.com/guide/?platform=mac&amp;product=ibooks&amp;vanityname=organize-and-sort-your-books&amp;version=1.11&amp;locale=en_US&amp;topicid=IBKS4B6D6F7A&amp;type=ddm&amp;platformOSVersion=10.13\" class=\"xRef AppleTopic\">Organize and sort your books</a></div></body>"}]},"categoryInfo":{"categories":["DisplayVersion/macOS High Sierra","platform/mac","ContentMode/liveContent","ExternalIndex/ExternalIndexOFF","ArchivalStatus/Unarchived","MetaFollow/MetaFollowOFF","SupportSearchIndex/SupportSearchIndexOFF"],"categoryDictionaries":[{"key":"liveContent","name":"Live Content","englishName":"Live Content","displayName":"Live Content","articleCount":"7864"},{"key":"Unarchived","name":"Unarchived","englishName":"Unarchived","displayName":"Unarchived","articleCount":"10186"},{"key":"ContentMode","name":"ContentMode","englishName":"ContentMode","displayName":"ContentMode","articleCount":"0"},{"key":"macOS High Sierra","name":"macOS High Sierra","englishName":"macOS High Sierra","displayName":"macOS High Sierra","articleCount":"2315"},{"key":"MetaFollow","name":"MetaFollow","englishName":"MetaFollow","displayName":"MetaFollow","articleCount":"0"},{"key":"ExternalIndex","name":"ExternalIndex","englishName":"ExternalIndex","displayName":"ExternalIndex","articleCount":"0"},{"key":"SupportSearchIndexOFF","name":"SupportSearchIndexOFF","englishName":"SupportSearchIndexOFF","displayName":"SupportSearchIndexOFF","articleCount":"6283"},{"key":"mac","name":"mac","englishName":"mac","displayName":"mac","articleCount":"7510"},{"key":"platform","name":"platform","en